Robustness checks for all birds phyla models

JQ meeting 29 April 2022 * plot raw data to check effects * arcsine square root transofmr + gaussian model as alt to binomial * can report original model in paper but mention potential over dispersion and that certain results are less robust and certain results more robust

set up

rr #install.packages()

library(MuMIn) library(arm) library(microbiome) library(dplyr) library(stringr) library(kableExtra)

rr mot <- readRDS(../Data/05_melted.phyla.glom.rds)

rr proteobacteria.df <- mot[mot$Phylum==,] firmicutes.df <- mot[mot$Phylum==,]

Proteobacteria

rr proteo.Proportion <- c(proteobacteria.df\(Abundance/proteobacteria.df\)NumberOfReads)

proteobacteria.df <- cbind(proteobacteria.df, proteo.Proportion)

rm(list = .Proportion)

check effects * Age * brood size * distance to edge * age x habitat * age x brood size * age x distance * age x lay date

rr ggplot(proteobacteria.df, aes(ageBinned, proteo.Proportion)) + geom_boxplot()

rr ggplot(proteobacteria.df, aes(broodSizeWhenSampled ,proteo.Proportion)) + # geom_smooth() + geom_smooth(method=) + geom_point()

rr

ggplot(subset(proteobacteria.df, broodSizeWhenSampled>1 & broodSizeWhenSampled<7), aes(broodSizeWhenSampled, proteo.Proportion)) + # geom_smooth() + geom_smooth(method=) + geom_point()

rr ggplot(proteobacteria.df, aes(DistanceToEdge ,proteo.Proportion)) + # geom_smooth() + geom_smooth(method=) + geom_point()

rr

ggplot(subset(proteobacteria.df, DistanceToEdge<50), aes(DistanceToEdge, proteo.Proportion)) + # geom_smooth() + geom_smooth(method=) + geom_point()

rr ggplot(proteobacteria.df, aes(ageBinned, proteo.Proportion, fill = habitat)) + geom_boxplot()

rr ggplot(proteobacteria.df, aes(as.factor(broodSizeWhenSampled), proteo.Proportion, fill = ageBinned)) + geom_boxplot()

rr ggplot((proteobacteria.df), aes(DistanceToEdge, proteo.Proportion, fill = ageBinned)) + # geom_smooth() + geom_smooth(method=) + geom_point()

rr

drop large distance values

ggplot(subset(proteobacteria.df, DistanceToEdge<50), aes(DistanceToEdge, proteo.Proportion, fill = ageBinned)) + # geom_smooth() + geom_smooth(method=) + geom_point()

ggplot(proteobacteria.df, aes(layDateFirst, proteo.Proportion, fill = ageBinned, label = nest)) +
  geom_smooth(method="lm") +
  geom_point() +
  geom_label()

proteobacteria.adult.df <- mot[(mot$Phylum=="Proteobacteria" & mot$ageBinned=="adult"),]
firmicutes.adult.df <- mot[(mot$Phylum=="Firmicutes" & mot$ageBinned=="adult"),]

proteo.Proportion <- c(proteobacteria.adult.df$Abundance/proteobacteria.adult.df$NumberOfReads)

proteobacteria.adult.df <- cbind(proteobacteria.adult.df, proteo.Proportion)

rm(list = "proteo.Proportion")
ggplot(proteobacteria.adult.df, aes(ageDays, proteo.Proportion)) +
  geom_boxplot()

ggplot(proteobacteria.adult.df, aes(broodSizeWhenSampled, proteo.Proportion)) +
 # geom_smooth() +
  geom_smooth(method="lm") +
  geom_point()

  geom_point()

 # geom_smooth() +
  geom_smooth(method="lm") +
  geom_point()

 # geom_smooth() +
  geom_smooth(method="lm") +
  geom_point()

ggplot(proteobacteria.adult.df, aes(habitat, proteo.Proportion)) +
